headline.print_headline: Union Recruit Former Manchester United Assistant Coach
headline.main: Union Recruit Former Manchester United Assistant Coach

lead_paragraph: The Philadelphia Union made another off-season move on Friday by appointing former Manchester United assistant coach Rene Meulensteen as a consultant, the Major League Soccer (MLS) team announced.
